title: RPG MAKER VX ACE DLC PACKS
description:
These are the dlc packs that i got from the humble bundle offer in july 2015 for the RPG MAKER VX ACE with some extra files added. This includes:

-Fantasy dlc
-Futuristic dlc
-RPG maker tutorials
-humble bundle 2015 init pack
-ModernDay_MusicMiniPack_RPGMakerDLCBundle1
-Steampunk_Western_PreviewPack_RPGMakerDLCBundle2
-JoelSteudler_AllMusicSampler_RPGMakerDLCBundle3
-LunaEngine
-NewDLCPack_bta
-StarterAssetPack

These DLC Packs includes a lot of Tile Sets, Monsters, Music, UI Settings and sprites.



Good luck and have fun.

If you like it then please support the original creators. Also please seed so everyone will be able to get this
